00:19:08.930 --> 00:19:12.250
And I think we need
to increasingly build

00:19:12.250 --> 00:19:14.540
a bridge to folks like
some of the people

00:19:14.540 --> 00:19:18.240
in this audience who know
how to manage data, capture

00:19:18.240 --> 00:19:21.620
data, and provide
simple access to people

00:19:21.620 --> 00:19:23.432
