what's happening

00:19:23.432 --> 00:19:25.640
in their homes, what's
happening in the world, what's

00:19:25.640 --> 00:19:28.960
happening with the companies
that they do business with.

00:19:28.960 --> 00:19:31.250
And I think this is
the recipe for change

00:19:31.250 --> 00:19:32.690
that we really
have to look at it.

00:19:32.690 --> 00:19:35.690
When I look at Clayoquot Sound,
the Great Bear Rainforest, oil

00:19:35.690 --> 00:19:37.490
