move millions of acres

00:19:43.670 --> 00:19:45.950
to protection,
change industries,

00:19:45.950 --> 00:19:48.890
and transparency has
been a big part of it.

00:19:48.890 --> 00:19:50.600
In the next decade,
you all know we

00:19:50.600 --> 00:19:52.460
have a huge challenge
in front of us

00:19:52.460 --> 00:19:55.400
with climate change
and many other issues.

00:19:55.400 --> 00:19:57.800
I think that to
the extent that we

00:19:57.800 --> 00:20:00.890
can get folks that are
campaigners working with folks

00:20:00.890 --> 00:20:05.660
that are coders with
common cause to try to map

00:20:05.660 --> 00:20:07.694
and provide access to
information for some

00:20:07.694 --> 00:20:09.110
