challenges, that's

00:20:09.110 --> 00:20:12.830
going to be how we provide
the world we want to hand off

00:20:12.830 --> 00:20:15.630
to our kids and to
the next generation.

00:20:15.630 --> 00:20:20.490
And here's to campaigners
and coders working together.

00:20:20.490 --> 00:20:22.835
