me time and again

00:33:17.350 --> 00:33:19.510
is that every time I go
to these conferences,

00:33:19.510 --> 00:33:20.560
and then we'd go out--

00:33:20.560 --> 00:33:23.530
some of us panelists
or attendees

00:33:23.530 --> 00:33:26.320
would go out to dinner,
and we'd go out.

00:33:26.320 --> 00:33:28.630
